- cs.SOC (Computational Social Science) is another possible category as the paper focuses on social network data. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is a possible category as the paper discusses truss index maintenance. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with graph theory concepts such as subgraphs and triangles.
